        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>chopped potato </strong>and <strong>diced carrot </strong>with the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>cannellini beans</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken stock </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until the veg is tender</p>",
