    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the veg is tender, remove the pot from the heat and stir through your <strong>soft</strong> <strong>cheese</strong> with a generous grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>creamy chorizo & bean stew</strong></p>",
